  "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
  "body": "`index.yaml` files provide a `digest` with a sha256 hash of the chart archive. Packages in OCI registries are content addressable (meaning we have a hash). When `helm pull` does it's work it should be possible to check what was downloaded against the hash for the version for the cases where a hash is available.\r\n\r\nThoughts?",
